b'This time, it\xe2\x80\x99s our shout.

From today, we will provide meals to hospitality workers impacted by COVID-19. We also recognise that businesses still open with takeaway and delivery options are in urgent need of support. While vouchers last, hospitality workers and businesses impacted by the COVID-19 crisis can access a daily $25 voucher with Deliveroo. To redeem, simply email MealsForMates@pernod-ricard.com with proof of employment in the hospitality industry.
Open to 18+ only. See link in bio for full terms and conditions. #MealsForMates :video_camera:: @thejamesadams @maclayheriot'
